NOIs are applications for permits filed with local Conservation Commission and MassDEP regional offices to dredge, remove, or alter wetlands. Filter by NOI number, project address, and filing date. You can also see who applied for the permit. This dataset is hosted in the Energy & Environmental Affairs Data Portal, an open data hub for state environmental data.
field_data_topic: Energy and Environment, Water
